com.spazedog.lib.rootfw4.utils

Class Memory.Swap

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.spazedog.lib.rootfw4.utils.Memory
      • com.spazedog.lib.rootfw4.utils.Memory.Swap
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Memory.CompCache
    Enclosing class:
    Memory

    public static class Memory.Swap
extends Memory
    This class is an extension of the Memory class. This can be used to get information about-, and handle swap and CompCache/ZRam devices.

      • getSwapDetails

        public Memory.SwapStat getSwapDetails()
        Get information like size and usage of a specific SWAP device. This method will return null if the device does not exist, or if it has not been activated.
        Parameters:
        device - The specific SWAP device path to get infomation about
        Returns:
        An SwapStat object containing information about the requested SWAP device
